s, for participating students, during the summer experience.<\/p><h3>WHY SHOULD HIGH SCHOOL STUDENTS APPLY?<\/h3><ul><li>Jump-start your career development.<\/li><li>Interact with professional mentors.<\/li><li>Gain leadership experience and training.<\/li><li>Enhance your resume or college application.<\/li><\/ul><h3>HOW DO I APPLY?<\/h3><ul><li>Review the available Enhanced Internship Opportunities and find ones that interest you. Experiences take place during the summer break.<\/li><li>Apply by May 9th.<\/li><li>Should an Employer be interested, you will be contacted.\u00a0 One day of Enhanced Internship interviews will take place at the high school.<\/li><li>If selected, the employer will require you to fill out their onboarding documents.\u00a0 In addition, you will need to submit an <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/BD-Enhanced-Internship-Agreement-Form.pdf\">Enhanced Internship Agreement Form<\/a><\/span> to info@beaverdamchamber.com.\u00a0<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b168840\" data-id=\"b168840\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bd2d68 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6bd2d68\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/beaverdamchamber.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/engineering.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"Engineering\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-96baf78 elementor-widget